Class TaskBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.com.cybersearch2.classytask.WorkerTask<Boolean>
      • au.com.cybersearch2.classyjpa.entity.TaskBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Executable, ThreadMessenger<Boolean>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PersistenceContainer.PersistenceTaskImpl

    public abstract class TaskBase
extends WorkerTask<Boolean>
    TaskBase Implements most of the details to execute a peristence WorkerTask. To complete, override base class method executeInBackground().
    Author:
    Andrew Bowley 19/08/2014
